FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://gamelookup.me/api

# GameLookup

GameLookup is your one-stop-shop for all you curious gamer needs.


## GameLookup Database [/search?{query}&{limit}]

### Search our Database [GET]

+ Parameters
    + query - query string
    + limit - number of returned items limit
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
         "Results": [
                {
                    "type": "Game",
                    "title": "Test game",
                    "route": "/games/1234",
                    "image": "image source"
                },
                {
                    "type": "Publisher",
                    "title": "Test Company",
                    "route": "/publishers/1234",
                    "image": "image source"  
                },
                {
                    "type": "Genre",
                    "title": "Test Genre",
                    "route": "/genre/1234",
                    "image": "image source"  
                }
            ]
        }


